            <div class="about-text">
                <h3>Hello, I'm Laura</h3>
                <p>Photography has always been my way of seeing the world differently—finding beauty in fleeting moments and preserving them forever. With over eight years of experience, I've had the privilege of capturing love stories, family milestones, and the quiet poetry of everyday life.</p>
                <p>My approach is gentle and unobtrusive. I believe the most authentic photographs emerge when people feel comfortable and free to be themselves. Whether it's the golden hour light cascading through a forest or the tender glance between two people in love, I seek out those magical, in-between moments.</p>
                <p>Based in the Pacific Northwest, I'm inspired daily by the soft, diffused light and natural landscapes that surround me. I'd love to hear your story and create something beautiful together.</p>
